Package: NEURICX
Type: Package
Title: Network-Enhanced Unified Rational Intelligence in Computational Economics
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("NEURICX", "Consortium", email = "neuricx@econresearch.ai", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive framework for network-enhanced economic modeling that integrates heterogeneous agent-based systems with multi-protocol communication. NEURICX provides tractable implementations of production networks, consumption networks, and information networks with empirical validation capabilities.
